    "The pipeline is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "It features an offline and an online component.",
    "The offline component (top, in green) consists of three main steps:",
    "➀ Preprocessing: a large cooking recipe database (RecipeNLG) is preprocessed to obtain the ratings for each recipe.",
    "We denote the resulting dataset of rated recipes as RELEXset."
